text: Picardia eparches is a moth of the family Pterophoridae. It is known from Kenya and Uganda. The wingspan is 20–25 mm.Beitrag zur Kenntnis der Pterophoridae-Fauna Kenyas (Lepidoptera) ==References== Category:Oidaematophorini Category:Moths of Africa Category:Moths described in 1931 Category:Taxa named by Edward Meyrick
